{"tid":720686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑X到肚痛] 西班牙文物局 找美術老師修復一尊500年前文物 令當地人民憤怒","createTime":"2018-06-28T06:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T07:26:57.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9f61aa4f76c22229d817c892a3bbfcc6e4703d","tid":720686,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/default/1_img/upload/3933d981/44/w540h304/20180627/2h8E-hencxtv2607176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fdefault%2F1_img%2Fupload%2F3933d981%2F44%2Fw540h304%2F20180627%2F2h8E-hencxtv2607176.jpg&h=b7c4c662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/default/1_img/upload/3933d981/280/w540h540/20180627/rCOj-hencxtv2607455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fdefault%2F1_img%2Fupload%2F3933d981%2F280%2Fw540h540%2F20180627%2FrCOj-hencxtv2607455.jpg&h=bea029a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修復前後對比圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/default/1_img/upload/3933d981/591/w540h851/20180627/oPww-hencxtv2608102.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fdefault%2F1_img%2Fupload%2F3933d981%2F591%2Fw540h851%2F20180627%2FoPww-hencxtv2608102.png&h=7d383edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在互聯網上，網友們鋪天蓋地地把修復後的雕像與卡通人偶進行對比。<br />\n<br />\n在西班牙北部納瓦拉地區（Navarra）埃斯泰拉鎮聖米格爾教堂（San Miguel of Estella），一名牧師拜託當地一名美術教師修復一尊16世紀的雕像，結果這尊雕像被&ldquo;修復&ldquo;成了卡通人偶，看到修復後的文物，人們都憤怒了。<br />\n<br />\n這尊聖喬治（聖喬治）的雕像展示了身穿盔甲的騎士騎著戰馬與巨龍搏鬥的場景。據報導，教堂的一名牧師何塞&middot;米格爾（Jose Miguel）覺得這尊尊500年前的文物掉漆脫色太嚴重了，他就詢問一位美術教師是否願意花時間來修復它，而沒有找專業的文物修復師。<br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體報導，著手修復的女教師名叫卡門（Carmen Usua），在當地一所學校教工藝美術。她很樂意幫忙，結果本週她展示了修復後的效果，讓當地居民大為不滿。"},{"pid":"8f7dbad9273c184becb1c1e728571c9c33e0970c","tid":720686,"uid":104443,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"係咪我審美觀嘅問題，我覺得佢修得幾靚"},{"pid":"0cd8d3a52fbff9427de1afa847ad7fd6692e5473","tid":720686,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:16:50.000Z","msg":"原畫咪又係咁卡通"},{"pid":"45cc376673c221cf9ad6093c348a7ce845274c8b","tid":720686,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得立體咗"},{"pid":"bea3a2ca150d930b69283f495328edd1ea23c4e1","tid":720686,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:29:50.000Z","msg":"過幾年開始甩甩地色/有陣殘舊味應該會順眼返"},{"pid":"b2d44f80e3b85daa8f4fe8a005f7163b7c78c41a","tid":720686,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"咁你地想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f0a393f67158374a7f741d1636f786de4c3445","tid":720686,"uid":44562,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ih0.redbubble.net/image.524624679.5938/flat,550x550,075,f.u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fih0.redbubble.net%2Fimage.524624679.5938%2Fflat%2C550x550%2C075%2Cf.u3.jpg&h=61b03d3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5ab630205a12776998bc1c46561f3f40821cb3a","tid":720686,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:38:45.000Z","msg":"本身原作個樣都好膠好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169ccab3bad766c5a75becd9ae400accb50b3868","tid":720686,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"搵架仔搞啦"},{"pid":"0ce0c8c21c77ef95c061e39f24686903cd37832e","tid":720686,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"好普通姐，耶穌果幅先勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6462d51eaa2e27cb67acee048315a975c5fe4610","tid":720686,"uid":1031